fields.description:
The following example will show {{undefined}} in the TextField while I'd expect it to be empty.

{code:javascript}
var win = Ti.UI.createWindow();
 
win.add(Ti.UI.createTextField({
	top: 100,
	height: 50,
        width: Ti.UI.FILL,
        value: undefined
}));
 
win.open();
{code}
